<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>北陸旅行</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1c1509;
    --brown: #3d2b1a;
    --gold: #a0813a;
    --gold-light: #c9a96e;
    --gold-pale: #e8d5a3;
    --paper: #f2e8d5;
    --paper-dark: #e6d8be;
    --paper-mid: #ddd0b0;
    --rust: #7a3b1e;
    --sepia: #5c4433;
    --muted: #7a6650;
    --faded: #9c8670;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: #0e0a04;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .flyer {
    max-width: 430px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--paper);
    position: relative;
    /* subtle paper texture via layered gradients */
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 28px,
        rgba(90,60,20,0.04) 28px,
        rgba(90,60,20,0.04) 29px
      ),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(180,140,60,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 80%, rgba(100,60,10,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .header {
    background: var(--brown);
    padding: 28px 18px 22px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--gold);
  }

  /* worn halftone-ish overlay */
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        transparent 0px,
        transparent 3px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 3px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 4px
      );
  }

  .header-stamp {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .stamp-box {
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 3px 18px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .stamp-box::before, .stamp-box::after {
    content: '◆';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 7px;
  }
  .stamp-box::before { left: -10px; }
  .stamp-box::after  { right: -10px; }

  .stamp-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 5px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .header-rule {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin: 10px 0 12px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .header-rule::before, .header-rule::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
  }
  .rule-diamond {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 10px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    position: relative;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .header-dates {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .header-dates::before, .header-dates::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(160,129,58,0.5));
  }
  .header-dates::before {
    background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(160,129,58,0.5));
  }

  .date-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-style: italic;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── BODY ── */
  .body {
    padding: 18px 14px 22px;
  }

  /* ── DAY SECTION ── */
  .day-section {
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .day-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    margin-bottom: 11px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .day-num-badge {
    background: var(--brown);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 48px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .day-num-big {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .day-title-block {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--paper-dark);
    padding: 7px 10px;
  }

  .day-title-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .day-title-jp {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brown);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .day-title-date {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .day-title-en {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--faded);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline {
    padding-left: 12px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--gold);
    margin-left: 10px;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 7px;
    position: relative;
    padding: 4px 0 4px 10px;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -4px;
    top: 10px;
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--paper);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .timeline-item.hl::before {
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .time-col {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-top: 1px;
  }

  .activity {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .timeline-item.hl .activity {
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .memo {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--sepia);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--paper-mid);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 0 4px;
    font-size: 9px;
    margin-right: 3px;
    color: var(--brown);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ── DAY DIVIDER ── */
  .day-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    margin: 2px 0 16px 4px;
  }
  .div-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      to right,
      var(--gold-pale) 0px,
      var(--gold-pale) 4px,
      transparent 4px,
      transparent 8px
    );
  }
  .div-ornament {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    background: var(--brown);
    border-top: 3px double var(--gold);
    padding: 12px 18px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-left {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(232,213,163,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .footer-center {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .f-diamond {
    width: 4px; height: 4px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .footer-right {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(232,213,163,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="flyer">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-stamp">
      <div class="stamp-box">
        <span class="stamp-text">Hokuriku Journey</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-rule"><div class="rule-diamond"></div></div>
    <h1>北　陸　旅　行</h1>
    <div class="header-dates">
      <span class="date-text">2025年 3月 28日（土）〜 30日（月）</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="body">

    <!-- DAY 1 -->
    <div class="day-section">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-num-badge">
          <span>Day</span>
          <span class="day-num-big">1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="day-title-block">
          <div class="day-title-row">
            <span class="day-title-jp">金沢観光</span>
            <span class="day-title-date">3/28 土</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-title-en">Kanazawa</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">09:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">金沢駅到着</div>
            <div class="memo">荷物・酒の冷蔵チェック</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">09:30–10:20</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">半月盆チェック ＋ 日本酒購入</div>
            <div class="memo">
              <span class="tag">漆器</span>創作漆器わこう（金沢百番街店）黒・マット・細金縁<br>
              <span class="tag">酒</span>遊穂（駅周辺）
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">10:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">ホテル荷物預け</div>
            <div class="memo">御宿 野乃 金沢</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">10:45–12:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">近江町市場 散策</div>
            <div class="memo">
              <span class="tag">漆器</span>輪島塗会館 金沢店<br>
              <span class="tag">酒</span>福光屋近江町店（試飲10分）<br>
              <span class="tag">つまみ</span>ほたるいか素干し・干し海老 / ガスエビ・ふぐのこ
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">13:00–14:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">ひがし茶屋街 散策</div>
            <div class="memo">
              <span class="tag">漆器</span>能加万菜 / アンティーク山屋 / 金沢美かざり / 箔一 東山店<br>
              <span class="tag">甘味</span>森八きんつば / 甘納豆かわむら
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">15:00–16:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">兼六園 観光</div>
            <div class="memo">桂坂口入園・霞ヶ池・徽軫灯籠</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item hl">
          <div class="time-col">16:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">夕食 ── もりもり寿し 片町店</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">夜</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">ホテルで部屋飲み</div>
            <div class="memo">遊穂・近江町つまみ・半月盆使用</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-divider">
      <div class="div-line"></div>
      <div class="div-ornament">✦ ✦ ✦</div>
      <div class="div-line"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- DAY 2 -->
    <div class="day-section">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-num-badge">
          <span>Day</span>
          <span class="day-num-big">2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="day-title-block">
          <div class="day-title-row">
            <span class="day-title-jp">永平寺・あわら温泉</span>
            <span class="day-title-date">3/29 日</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-title-en">Eiheiji & Awara Onsen</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">06:30–07:45</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">起床・朝食</div>
            <div class="memo">御宿 野乃にて</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">08:15–09:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">チェックアウト・レンタカー出発</div>
            <div class="memo">金沢 → 永平寺（約90km・1時間45分）</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item hl">
          <div class="time-col">11:00–12:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">永平寺 拝観</div>
            <div class="memo">山門 → 仏殿 → 法堂 → 傘松閣 → 回廊</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">12:45–13:45</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">昼食 ── おろし蕎麦</div>
            <div class="memo">けんぞう蕎麦（永平寺から車で約10分）</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">14:00–15:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">鳴鹿大堰 寄り道 → あわら温泉</div>
            <div class="memo">休憩10分後、移動約50分</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">15:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">チェックイン ── あわら温泉 清風荘</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">15:30–17:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">温泉街散策</div>
            <div class="memo">足湯・街歩き</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item hl">
          <div class="time-col">17:30–18:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">夕食 ── 清風荘 会席料理</div>
            <div class="memo">温泉・部屋でゆったりとした夜</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-divider">
      <div class="div-line"></div>
      <div class="div-ornament">✦ ✦ ✦</div>
      <div class="div-line"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- DAY 3 -->
    <div class="day-section">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-num-badge">
          <span>Day</span>
          <span class="day-num-big">3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="day-title-block">
          <div class="day-title-row">
            <span class="day-title-jp">恐竜博物館・帰路</span>
            <span class="day-title-date">3/30 月</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-title-en">Dinosaur Museum & Return</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">06:30–08:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">起床・朝食・チェックアウト</div>
            <div class="memo">清風荘にて。車で移動スタート</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item hl">
          <div class="time-col">10:00–12:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">福井県立恐竜博物館 見学</div>
            <div class="memo">巨大骨格・復元模型・ドーム展示（あわらから約1時間15分）</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item hl">
          <div class="time-col">12:30–13:30</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">昼食 ── ヨーロッパ軒 総本店</div>
            <div class="memo">福井名物ソースカツ丼・元祖の味</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">13:30–16:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">福井 → 金沢（移動・レンタカー返却）</div>
            <div class="memo">約2時間。金沢駅周辺で返却</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="time-col">16:30–17:00</div>
          <div class="content-col">
            <div class="activity">帰路 ── サンダーバード ＋ 新幹線</div>
            <div class="memo">金沢駅 → 大宮 / 19:30〜20:00 帰宅</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /body -->

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-left">金沢 · 永平寺 · あわら · 福井</div>
    <div class="footer-center">
      <div class="f-diamond"></div>
      <div class="f-diamond"></div>
      <div class="f-diamond"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">Mar 28–30, 2025</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
